"--- Dictionary Test ---" >> Display.
{"name": "Alice", "age": 25} >> dict1.
dict1 & "name" >> Get >> Display.
"Alice's age is {age}" & dict1 >> Format >> Display.

"--- Parallel Processing (Fork/Join) Test ---" >> Display.
["https://api.github.com/users/octocat", "https://api.github.com/users/torvalds"] >> fork:
    url.
    "{0} を取得中..." & url >> Format >> Display.
    url >> Fetch >> FromJson.
.. >> users.
users >> Length >> len.
"取得完了: {0} ユーザー" & len >> Format >> Display.

"--- Error Handling Test ---" >> Display.
"https://invalid-url-that-does-not-exist" >> Fetch >> catch:
    err.
    err & "type" >> Get >> type.
    err & "message" >> Get >> msg.
    "エラーを捕捉しました: [{0}] {1}" & type & msg >> Format >> Display.
    "エラー時の代替データ". // fallback value
.. >> fallback.

"フォールバック結果: {0}" & fallback >> Format >> Display.

"すべてのテストが完了しました！" >> Display.
